(swD sMgq ivc pRBU dI is&q-swlwh kr ky) jo mnu`K ijaUNdw hI mrdw hY ('dunIAw' vloN moh qoVdw hY) aus nUM iPr ieh sihm nhIN rihMdw ]29]
hy kbIr! mnu`Kw jnm bVI muSkl nwl imldw hY, (qy, jy pRBU dw nwm ivswr ky inrw 'dunIAw' ivc l`g ky ie`k vwrI h`QoN igAw) qW muV muV nhIN imldw;
ijvyN jMgl dy ru`KW dy p`ky hoey Pl (jdoN) zmIn auqy if`g pYNdy hn qW muV fwlI nwl nhIN l`gdy ]30]
(ies mnu`Kw jnm dw Asl mnorQ 'prmwqmw dy nwm dI pRwpqI' hY, ies dI ^wqr ieh zrUrI hY ik prmwqmw dw ismrn kIqw jwey, pRBU dy gux jwey jwx; so) hy kbIr! (sdw ieauN AwK-hy pRBU!) qUM hI sB qoN v`fw hYN, qyrw hI nwm sB qoN v`fw hY[
(pr ies is&q-swlwh dy nwl nwl hy kbIr!) jy qUM pihlW Awpxy srIr dw moh BI iqAwgyN, qdoN hI prmwqmw dw nwm-rUp rqn imldw hY ]31]
hy kbIr! ('srIr qjx' dw Bwv ieh hY ik 'dunIAw' dI ^wqr) igly-guzwrI nwh krdy rihEy, ('dunIAw' dy lwlc ivc PisAw hoieAw) jo kuJ qUM AwKdw hYN auhI nhIN ho skdw,
(is&q-swlwh krn dy nwl nwl ieh BI XkIn r`K ik) b^SS krn vwly pRBU jI jo b^SSW (jIvW auqy) krdy hn auhnW nUM koeI (hor jIv) vDw-Gtw nhIN skdw ]32]
hy kbIr! jo mnu`K 'dunIAw' nwl moh krn vwlw hY auh aus ksOtI auqy Krw swbq nhIN huMdw ijs dI rwhIN mnu`K dI pRBU nwl s`cI pRIq prKI jWdI hY[
pRBU nwl pRIq dI prK ivc auhI mnu`K pUrw auqrdw hY jo 'dunIAw' dy moh vloN mr ky 'dIn' dy ipAwr ivc jIaU ipAw hY ]33]
hy kbIr! (inrI 'dunIAw' dy vpwrI bMdy Awpxy Awp dI SUkw-SwkI vwsqy) vDIAw k`pVy pWdy hn qy pwn supwrIAW KWdy hn;
pr (srIr nUM sjweI r`Kx dy moh nwl) b`Jy hoey auh bMdy mOq Awidk dy sihm ivc itky rihMdy hn ikauNik auh prmwqmw dy nwm qoN vWjy rihMdy hn ('dIn' ivswr ky 'dunI' dw moh hr hwlq ivc duKdweI hY) ]34]
hy kbIr! jy iek bhuq hI purwxw jhwz hovy, ijs ivc hzwrW hI Cyk Pu`t pey hox,
(auh Aw^r smuMdr ivc fu`b hI jWdw hY, ies jhwz dy musw&irW ivcoN) isr& auhI bMdy qr ky pwr lMG jWdy hn ijn@W ny koeI Bwr nhIN cu`ikAw huMdw; pr ijMnHW dy isrW auqy Bwr huMdw hY, auh (Bwr hyT d`b ky) fu`b jWdy hn ]35]
('dIn' nUM ivswr ky inrI 'dunIAw' dI ^wqr dOV-B`j kridAW mnu`K Awpxy srIr dy moh ivc ieqnw Psdw hY ik hr vyly mOq qoN sihimAw rihMdw hY[ iPr BI, ieh srIr sdw kwiem nhIN rih skdw, mOq Aw hI jWdI hY, qdoN) hy kbIr! (srIr nUM icKw qy pwieAW) h`f l`kVW vWg sVdy hn, kys Gwh vWg sVdy hn[
ies swry sMswr nUM hI sVidAW vyK ky (Bwv, ieh vyK ky ik sB jIvW dw ies srIr nwloN ivCoVw Aw^r zrUr huMdw hY) mYN kbIr ies srIr dy moh qoN auprwm ho igAw hW (mYN srIr dw moh C`f id`qw hY) ]36]
hy kbIr! (ies srIr dI juAwnI suMdrqw Awidk dw) mwx nhIN krnw cwhIdw (Aw^r hY qW ieh) h`fIAW (dI mu`T) jo cMm nwl lpytIAW hoeIAW hn[
(ies srIr dw AhMkwr krdy) auh bMdy BI (AMq nUM) im`tI ivc jw rly jo vDIAw GoiVAW au~qy (svwr huMdy sn) qy jo (Juldy) CqrW hyT bYTdy sn ]37]
hy kbIr! Awpxw au~cw mhl vyK ky (BI) AhMkwr nhIN krnw cwhIdw (ieh BI cwr idn dI hI Kyf hY;
mOq Awaux qy ies mhl nUM C`f ky) A`j Blk hI im`tI ivc rl jwxw hY, swfy (srIr) auqy Gwh au~g peygw ]38]
hy kbIr! (jy qUM Dnvwn hYN, qW ies Dn-pdwrQ dw BI) mwx nwh krIN, nwh iksy kMgwl nUM (vyK ky) T`Tw-m^Ol krIN[
(qyrI AwpxI jIvn-) byVI Ajy smuMdr ivc hY, pqw nhIN kIh ho jwey (ieh Dn-pdwrQ h`QoN jWidAW icr nhIN l`gdw) ]39]
hy kbIr! ies sohxy rMg vwly srIr nUM vyK ky BI AhMkwr nwh krIey;
ieh srIr BI QohVy idnW ivc hI C`f jwaugy ijvyN s`p kuMj lwh dyNdw hY (ijMd qy srIr dw BI p`kw sdw-inBvW swQ nhIN hY) ]40]
hy kbIr! ('dunIAw' dI ^wqr kIh Btk irhw hYN? vyK) prmwqmw dw nwm dbw-db vMifAw jw irhw hY, jy iek`Tw krnw hY qW ieh nwm-Dn iek`Tw kr[
jdoN ijMd (srIr ivcoN) inkl geI, smW ivhw jwx qy A&sos krnw peygw ]41]
(pr nwm Dn iek`Tw krn leI zrUrI hY ik mnu`K Apx`q nUM pihlW ^qm kry, qy) hy kbIr! (jgq ivc) Aijhw koeI ivrlw hI imldw hY jo Awpxy srIrk moh nUM swVdw hY,
qy, kwmwidk mwieAw dy pMjW hI pu`qRW nUM swV ky prmwqmw (dI Xwd) ivc surq joVI r`Kdw hY ]42]
koeI ivrlw hI huMdw hY jo prmwqmw nwl (aus dy nwm dw) vxj krdw hY, jo (nwm Dn ^rIdx leI kwmwidk mwieAw dy pMj) pu`qR Aqy (AwSw iqRSnw eIrKw Awidk) DIAW v`ty ivc dyNdw hY[
kbIr cwhuMdw hY ik Ajyhw mnu`K (ies vpwr ivc) myry nwl BI sq-sMg dI sWJ bxwey ]43]
hy kbIr! mYN qYnUM cyqw krWdw hW, mqW iPr gumr rih jwey;
jo Bog hux qweIN qUM Bogy hn (mqW smJyN ik qUM bVIAW mOjW mwx leIAW hn, Asl ivc) iehnW dI pWieAW ieqnI ku hI hY (ijvyN iksy h`tI qoN sOdw lY ky JUMgy vjoN) rqw ku guV lY ky Kw leyN ]44]
hy kbIr! (ieQy kwSI ivc au~cIAW jwqW vwilAW nUM vyd SwsqR Awidk pVHidAW vyK ky) mYN smiJAw sI ik iv`idAw pVHnI mnu`Kw jnm dw sB qoN cMgw kMm hovygw, pr (iehnW lokW dy inry vwd ivvwd vyK ky mYnUM XkIn Aw igAw hY ik AjyhI iv`idAw) pVHn nwloN pRBU-crnW ivc juVnw (mnu`K leI) Blw hY[
(so, ies g`loN) jgq by-S`k mYnUM mwVw ipAw AwKy mYN (iv`idAw dy v`ty BI) prmwqmw dI BgqI nhIN C`fWgw ]45]
hy kbIr! ijs mnu`K dy AMdr (ieh) sUJ nhIN hY (ik iv`idAw dy twkry qy pRBU dI BgqI ikqnI vf-mu`lI dwq hY, auh mnu`K jy myrI ies cox qy mYnUM mwVw AwKy) qW aus mnu`K dy ieh inMdw krn dw koeI ArQ nhIN hY[
so, kbIr (Ajyhy bMidAW dI ies dMd-kQw dI prvwh nhIN krdw, qy) prmwqmw dw ismrn kr irhw hY, Aqy hor swry (kMmW dy) moh dw iqAwg kr irhw hY ]46]
ies prdysI jIv dy igAwn-ieMidRAW nUM hr pwsy vloN ivkwrW dI A`g l`gI hoeI hY,
(jo prdysI jogI by-prvwh ho ky ies A`g dw in`G mwxdw irhw, aus dI) srIr-godVI (ivkwrW dI A`g ivc) sV ky koly ho geI, (pr ijs prdysI jogI ny ies godVI dy Dwgy dw, ies srIr ivc v`sdI ijMd dw, ^iAwl r`iKAw qy ivkwr-AgnI dy in`G dw suAwd mwxn qoN sMkoc kIqI r`iKAw, aus dI) Awqmw nUM (iehnW ivkwrW dI A`g dw) syk BI nwh l`gw (Bwv, auh ies bldI A`g ivcoN bc igAw) ]47]
hy kbIr! (ivkwrW dI A`g ivc pY ky ijs bd-nsIb jIv-jogI dI) srIr-godVI sV ky kolw ho geI qy (ijs dw) mn-K`pr dr dr qoN vwsnW dI iB`iCAw hI iek`TI krdw irhw,
(auh) mMd-BwgI jIv-jogI mnu`Kw jnm dI Kyf aujwV ky hI jWdw hY, aus dy p`ly Kyh-^uAwrI hI pYNdI hY ]48]
